com.concordium.sdk.transactions

Class CredentialDeploymentTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.concordium.sdk.transactions.BlockItem
      • com.concordium.sdk.transactions.CredentialDeploymentTransaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Transaction

    public class CredentialDeploymentTransaction
extends BlockItem
    CredentialDeploymentTransaction used to deploy new account credentials on chain. This type of transaction is not paid by the sender and bakers are compensated by the protocol.
